---
description: Codentra core engineering rules
alwaysApply: true
---

- Monorepo: pnpm workspaces + Turborepo
- Backend: NestJS feature modules at apps/api/src/features/
- Frontend: Next.js 15 App Router at apps/web/src/features/
- Prisma schema at apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma — single source of truth
- Strict TypeScript — no `any`
- API: /api/v1 with envelope { success, data } or { success: false, error }
- Auth: JWT in httpOnly cookies via BFF /api/proxy/* (target architecture)
- Every feature: validation, loading states, empty states, mobile responsive
- Update docs/TASKS.md and docs/CHANGELOG.md after each completed feature
- Build phases in order — never skip ahead
- Conventional commits: feat(scope): description
- Minimal diff — match patterns, no over-engineering
